description:
Jesus had gone to the other side of the lake to get some rest. But instead, he received a noisy and dramatic welcome. What does the story of the demon-possesed man tell us about the harm our sins can cause? And what does it show about Jesus' attitude to those who seem hopelessly entangled in sin? Find out here.
